fica di {slogan} sopra una pizza su sfondo arancione con logo Just Eat sotto","consumerWebHome.sections.heroImage.cheeseburgerAlt_ch":"Grafica di {slogan} sopra un hamburger con patatine fritte e ketchup su sfondo arancione con logo {brandName} sotto","consumerWebHome.sections.heroImage.falafelSaladAlt_be":"Grafica di {slogan} sopra una ciotola di falafel e verdura su sfondo arancione con logo {brandName} sotto","consumerWebHome.sections.heroImage.cheeseburgerAlt_be":"Grafica di {slogan} sopra un hamburger con patatine fritte e ketchup su sfondo arancione con logo {brandName} sotto","consumerWebHome.sections.heroImage.falafelSaladAlt_ch":"Grafica di {slogan} sopra una ciotola di falafel e verdura su sfondo arancione con logo {brandName} sotto","consumerWebHome.sections.heroImage.margheritaPizzaAlt_ch":"Grafica di {slogan} sopra una pizza su sfondo arancione con logo {brandName} sotto","consumerWebHome.sections.heroImage.margheritaPizzaAlt_be":"Grafica di {slogan} sopra una pizza su sfondo arancione con logo {brandName} sotto","consumerWebHome.seo.tags.title":"{siteName} | Consegna cibo a domicilio | Ordina pizza, sushi e altro online","consumerWebHome.modal.emailChangeConfirmationPage.title":"Modifica la tua email","consumerWebHome.modal.emailChangeConfirmationPage.submitButton":"Modifica email","consumerWebHome.modal.emailChangeConfirmationPage.content":"Inserisci la password per confermare che desideri sostituire la precedente email con {email}.","consumerWebHome.modal.forgotPasswordResetConfirmationPage.title":"Password dimenticata?","consumerWebHome.modal.forgotPasswordResetConfirmationPage.changePasswordButton":"Cambia password","consumerWebHome.campaigns.cocaCola.title":"E per i brindisi? C'è la Coca-Cola","consumerWebHome.campaigns.cocaCola.subtitle":"Inserisci il tuo indirizzo per il tocco frizzante che illumina le feste, sorso dopo sorso","consumerWebHome.campaigns.spriteTinder.title":"Spice is your thing. Complete your menu with Sprite's","consumerWebHome.campaigns.spriteTinder.subtitle":"Find restaurants and shops that deliver to you","consumerWebHome.campaigns.cokeTheatre.title":"Have a Coca-Cola on us","consumerWebHome.campaigns.cokeTheatre.subtitle":"Get Match Day Ready with a FREE Coca-Cola","consumerWebAfterOrder.markdownTest.markdownTest.markdownTest":"Sample Markdown text in English (also available in Dutch)\r\n\r\n# h1 Heading\r\n## h2 Heading\r\n### h3 Heading\r\n#### h4 Heading\r\n##### h5 Heading\r\n###### h6 Heading\r\n\r\n\r\n## Horizontal Rules\r\n\r\n___\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n***\r\n\r\n## Emphasis\r\n\r\n**This is bold text**\r\n\r\n__This is bold text__\r\n\r\n*This is italic text*\r\n\r\n_This is italic text_\r\n\r\n~~Strikethrough~~\r\n\r\n\r\n## Blockquotes\r\n\r\n\r\n\u003e Blockquotes can also be nested...\r\n\u003e\u003e ...by using additional greater-than signs right next to each other...\r\n\u003e \u003e \u003e ...or with spaces between arrows.\r\n\r\n\r\n## Lists\r\n\r\nUnordered\r\n\r\n+ Create a list by starting a line with `+`, `-`, or `*`\r\n+ Sub-lists are made by indenting 2 spaces:\r\n  - Marker character change forces new list start:\r\n    * Ac tristique libero volutpat at\r\n    + Facilisis in pretium nisl aliquet\r\n    - Nulla volutpat aliquam velit\r\n+ Very easy!\r\n\r\nOrdered\r\n\r\n1. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet\r\n2. Consectetur adipiscing elit\r\n3. Integer molestie lorem at massa\r\n\r\n\r\n1. You can use sequential numbers...\r\n1. ...or keep all the numbers as `1.`\r\n\r\nStart numbering with offset:\r\n\r\n57. foo\r\n1. bar\r\n\r\n\r\n## Code\r\n\r\nInline `code`\r\n\r\nIndented code\r\n\r\n    // Some comments\r\n    line 1 of code\r\n    line 2 of code\r\n    line 3 of code\r\n\r\n\r\nBlock code \"fences\"\r\n\r\n```\r\nSample text here...\r\n```\r\n\r\nSyntax highlighting\r\n\r\n``` js\r\nvar foo = function (bar) {\r\n  return bar++;\r\n};\r\n\r\nconsole.log(foo(5));\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Tables\r\n\r\n| Option | Description |\r\n| ------ | ----------- |\r\n| data   | path to data files to supply the data that will be passed into templates. |\r\n| engine | engine to be used for processing templates. Handlebars is the default. |\r\n| ext    | extension to be used for dest files. |\r\n\r\nRight aligned columns\r\n\r\n| Option | Description |\r\n| ------:| -----------:|\r\n| data   | path to data files to supply the data that will be passed into templates. |\r\n| engine | engine to be used for processing templates. Handlebars is the default. |\r\n| ext    | extension to be used for dest files. |\r\n\r\n\r\n## Links\r\n\r\n[link text](https://www.thuisbezorgd.nl)\r\n\r\n[link with title](https://www.thuisbezorgd.nl \"Order Food\")\r\n\r\n\r\n## Images\r\n\r\n![Minion](https://octodex.github.com/images/minion.png)\r\n\r\n![Stormtroopocat](https://octodex.github.com/images/stormtroopocat.jpg \"The Stormtroopocat\")","consumerWebAfterOrder.ukraineBanner.icon.thankYouText":"Grazie","consumerWebAfterOrder.ukraineBanner.content.title":"Globalmente, abbiamo donato 2M€.","consumerWebAfterOrder.ukraineBanner.content.cta":"Dona ancora","consumerWebAfterOrder.ukraineBanner.content.footer":"Si applicano T\u0026C + politiche UNHCR.","consumerWebAfterOrder.test.test.test":"test","consumerWebAfterOrder.orderConfirmationPage.foodTracker.shareFoodtrackerUrl":"Condividi il link di tracciamento","consumerWebAfterOrder.orderConfirmationPage.feedback.title":"Aiutaci a migliorare questa pagina","consumerWebAfterOrder.orderConfirmationPage.feedback.description":"Vorremmo conoscere la tua opinione su questa pagina. Ci vorrà solo un minuto.","consumerWebAfterOrder.orderConfirmationPage.feedback.buttonLabel":"Lascia una recensione","consumerWebAfterOrder.orderConfirmationPage.trackOrder.header":"A breve potrai seguire l’ordine…","consumerWebAfterOrder.orderConfirmationPage.trackOrder.description":"Potrai seguire il tuo ordine sulla mappa non appena sarà partito.","consumerWebAfterOrder.orderConfirmationPage.pageNotFound.title":"Spiacenti, non abbiamo accesso a ques